Titolo: Mad Father

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Mad Father (Japanese: マッドファーザー, Hepburn: Maddofāzā) is a survival horror role-playing puzzle video game. The game was developed by Japanese developer Sen, published by Miscreant's Room and released on 10 December 2012. The game centers around an 11-year-old girl named Aya, who breaks into her father's secret laboratory to uncover the horrifying truth of his research. A Steam version, published by AGM Playism, was released on 23 September 2016.